result.title: Souvenirs of VK Cup 2017
result.content: I participated in VK Cup 2017 online mirror (Codeforces Round #424) about three months ago.And luckily I became one of the five random contestants to win the VK Cup 2017 souvenir.However,I haven't been contacted by anyone till now.So could anyone please tell me whether I'm ignored by admin or there exists other reasons for it?Thanks a lot!
